Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Software
Sub-Industry: Application Software
Zylo, Inc. owns and operates a software-as-a-service (SaaS) optimization platform. The Company, through its platform, manages cloud-based applications. Zylo serves customers in the United States.




